"{\"content\":{\"body\":\"Decentralized finance, or DeFi, has become one of the fastest-growing sectors within the cryptocurrency ecosystem. Data [shows](https://dappradar.com/) that the total value locked (TVL) in all DeFi protocols is now around $130 billion. This is an important metric, as some analysts view TVL as one of the best ways to [measure sentiment within the DeFi sector](https://cointelegraph.com/news/defi-tvl-hits-a-record-157b-as-ethereum-competitors-attract-investors). \\n\\nWhile growth is apparent, many individuals may still wonder what DeFi is and how it can be applied today. Piers Ridyard, chief executive officer of Radix DLT — a secure decentralized network — stated that DeFi currently [only caters to users with sufficient knowledge](https://cointelegraph.com/news/decentralized-finance-may-be-the-future-but-education-is-still-lacking) of the crypto market.\\n\\nThis in mind, it’s notable that a small number of universities are now offering DeFi-focused courses to help educate enrolled students and the general public on the basics of decentralized systems.\",\"timestamp\":1639035511,\"title\":\"DeFi literacy: Universities embrace decentralized finance education\"},\"digest\":\"_gTaKoTNn3z2s246PyulVXUMn4LaWKqTuookDd_I72E\",\"authorship\":{\"contributor\":\"0x9E1eD0a565710397B9d0Fb0716dCBe1eC41fdbD8\",\"signingKey\":\"{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\\\"verify\\\"],\\\"kty\\\":\\\"EC\\\",\\\"x\\\":\\\"asy-zcQvgN0cJLMxowtbM4LMgZXODdDCEkaL1RjpDOU\\\",\\\"y\\\":\\\"mdLxHFn7OH7SBvCz14LlvPuk-muQb8S5LSrou0ogAx0\\\"}\",\"signature\":\"L391dWArm8nlmuzD_w9JK-DjeUWODLOCtXZkJNMcMr2AUGRpnCwGOjICU6g4wUE_q6FVjQjXe_gsMjv3laBvEA\",\"signingKeySignature\":\"0xd42bfa31586071b855020eee8b2b467cbdb1c1f0f118b44ac3935178c9531cc6635d20aed89ab8714a5d9c916f0dfccb3a134661a72182d5527a7d5ce10978ca1b\",\"signingKeyMessage\":\"I authorize publishing on mirror.xyz from this device using:\\n{\\\"crv\\\":\\\"P-256\\\",\\\"ext\\\":true,\\\"key_ops\\\":[\